        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "“Rather than offering information or analysis on the safety programs, community outreach initiatives or other efforts taken by firearm and ammunition companies, these firms operate under blind standards with no disclosure of our industry’s extensive ESG work,” he wrote.",
