      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "With government paralyzed, divestment movements have become a popular, effective way for activists to voice their dissatisfaction with corporate behavior. In recent years, such movements have cut into the profits of increasingly unpopular industries such as private prisons, fossil fuels and firearms.",
